  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine the rate of diffusion weighted (DW)-MRI cerebral
      lesions following a Pulmonary Vein Ablation Catheter (PVAC) ablation procedure performed
      using best practices, including optimized procedural techniques and anti-coagulation therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
